title: The S-Stain Story
description: Two Sides to Every Date, Mixtape Game with guest Metra!, Dave asks us if he's the jerk about something he posted on a Facebook page, Tina's Celeb Dine and Dash, Dave has a conundrum about whether he should tell a certain story for the couple he's marrying this weekend, and more!
